      geo:long ?caplong .
  }
}
ORDER BY ?country

  ?country rdf:type dbo:Country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?nombre.
  ?country a <http://schema.org/Organization>.
  ?country rdfs:label ?team.
 
FILTER(lang(?nombre)="es").
FILTER regex((?nombre), "chile","i") .
}
ORDER BY ?country

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?name ?rank ?country ?bandera (COUNT(?team) AS ?num_jugadores) 
WHERE { 
?team rdfs:label ?name. 
?team dbpprop:fifaRank ?rank.
OPTIONAL {?team dbpprop:name ?num_jugadores}
OPTIONAL {?team dbo:thumbnail ?bandera.}

OPTIONAL {?team foaf:name ?country. }

OPTIONAL {FILTER (langMatches(lang(?country), "en")).}
FILTER ( lang(?name) = "en" )
FILTER (?rank <= 50 && langMatches(lang(?name),"en")
       && !REGEX(str(?name), "women", "i") && !REGEX(str(?name), "futsal", "i"))
}
GROUP BY ?team ?name ?rank ?country ?bandera
ORDER BY ?rank

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?name ?rank ?country ?bandera (COUNT(?team) AS ?num_jugadores) 
WHERE { 
?team rdfs:label ?name. 
?team dbpprop:fifaRank ?rank.
OPTIONAL {?team dbpprop:name ?num_jugadores}
OPTIONAL {?team dbo:thumbnail ?bandera.}

OPTIONAL {?team foaf:name ?country. }

OPTIONAL {FILTER (langMatches(lang(?country), "en")).}
FILTER ( lang(?name) = "en" )
FILTER (?rank <= 50 && langMatches(lang(?name),"en")
       && !REGEX(str(?name), "women", "i") && !REGEX(str(?name), "futsal", "i"))
}
GROUP BY ?team ?name ?rank ?country ?bandera
ORDER BY ?rank

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?jugador ?clubes ?ground ?pais
WHERE { 

?jugador a dbo:SoccerPlayer.
?jugador rdfs:label ?jugadornom.
OPTIONAL {?jugador dbprop:clubs ?clubes.}
OPTIONAL {?clubes dbo:ground ?ground.  }
OPTIONAL {?ground dbo:country ?pais.  FILTER EXISTS {?pais dbo:country  }.}


FILTER regex((?jugadornom), "alexis sánchez","i") 


}
ORDER BY ?jugador
